node.text:
Drawing an oc ✏️✨ You might’ve seen my purple sketch version of this drawing a few days ago and now I’m working on an alternate version! 🥰 It’s fun to explore the same drawing using different colors to explore various moods ✨ do you ever create multiple variations of the same drawing? 💭

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️

#reels #artreels #drawingreels #drawing #artprocess #drawingprocess #digitalart #digitalillustration #characterdesign #oc #characterart #ipadpro #ipadproart #ipadart #ipaddrawing #procreate #procreateart

node.text:
Some starry art 🌟 I’ve always loved incorporating stars into my work for some reason, they’re just so satisfying to draw! I used to doodle them all over my school notebooks and now they’re in my drawings too 🙈 What kind of things do you like to doodle? ✨

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️

Mulan 🐉✨ I love this Disney princess and had so much fun drawing her different looks! 🥰 Process video of this drawing will be going up on Patreon soon! Link is in my bio 💌✨ Which Mulan look is your fav? 🌼

Playing with colors on a sketch 🌟 I posted a step-by-step tutorial of this sketch and it’s up on Patreon! Link is in my bio 💌 I rarely use purple in my work nowadays but I find it so soothing & magical to work with 🥰 is there a certain color you love working with?✨

Sketching some fox studies 🦊✨ I love taking little breaks from drawing characters to study other subject matter occasionally, just to refresh my creativity 😌 and I find animals so relaxing to draw! 🌼 This week I’m working on a step-by-step tutorial for Patreon about how to draw foxes so this is fun practice! 🥰 What do you do to refresh your creativity? ✨

I make tutorials & drawing videos on my Patreon! 💌 Once you join you’ll get access to over 50+ tutorial videos & step-by-steps, real-time process videos, cozy draw with me videos, my custom brush set, studio vlogs, & more ✨ the link is in my bio! ☁️
